bookAuthors: Thomas Hardy, Patricia Ingham, Dennis Taylor, Jenny Sterlin, Mark Oxford, James Oliver Smith Jr.
plot: Jude Fawley's hopes of a university education are lost when he is trapped into marrying the earthy Arabella, who later abandons him. Moving to the town of Christminster where he finds work as a stonemason, Jude meets and falls in love with his cousin Sue Bridehead, a sensitive, freethinking 'New Woman'.
characters: Jude Fawley, Arabella Donn, Sue Bridehead
